{"tid":858373,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解人類會咁？","createTime":"2018-10-11T18:17:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T18:28:21.000Z","uid":158256,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67e8ec6c1ef58ba13e7510d938fae272f29c9c49","tid":858373,"uid":158256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T18:17:33.000Z","msg":"點解淨係識為自己爭取所有利益<br />\n但係可以唔理其他人？<br />\n真係覺得個地球圍住自己轉？<br />\n點解唔可以所有人都犧牲自己少少利益<br />\n令到自己同身邊所有人從中都得到其他人所犧牲既利益？<br />\n主角唔係你自己<br />\n而係係世界上既時刻<br />\n點解思維要咁狹窄唔可以睇開D<br />\n為咗利益而要發生衝突<br />\n因為個人情緒要傷害所有唔屬於自己既事物<br />\n完全唔識操控自己既依個個體<br />\n為求私人滿足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好常試跟住我所講既方法生存<br />\n但係係某d時侯又打回原形<br />\n點解會做唔到？<br />\n人點解會咁？<br />\n咁自私？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efdc62d73d0a63c7bb693ab661167a36fed9f94","tid":858373,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T18:25:35.000Z","msg":"3成人正常/叻,7成人弱智/仆街<br />\n愛因斯坦講既"},{"pid":"fc686e0c819e07eea0910f158f5a38df8f69235f","tid":858373,"uid":211528,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T18:28:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}